| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2021-1035 — Recovery Inhibition (dispossessor)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 27e57c51-f4ad-5d52-b3d4-e48155b089bd"
